title: Sidefeel Womens Wide Leg Jeans Casual Baggy High Waisted Stretch Denim Pants
description: Features: Fashion jean features wide leg, high waisted, four pockets, pinched seams, loose fit, double-breasted button and zipper fly closure and full length design. The unique pinched seams detail adds a touch of individuality

Design: Wide leg jean could flatter a variety of leg types, providing ample room for movement and breathability. They're a versatile and practical addition to any wardrobe, making styling easier with their all-match loose fit denim pants style

Style: Baggy denim pants are the key to creating effortless style, and our loose jeans are perfect for anyone. They're both suitable for everyday wear and for dressing up, and can be easily paired with a tank top, T-shirt, blouse, high heels, and more

Material: Crafted from comfortable materials, our wide leg jeans offer both comfort and a trendy, baggy style that's perfect for many occasions. Flattering wide-leg jean with sturdy and durable denim material ensures long-lasting wear

Occasions: Wide leg jeans are the perfect addition to your wardrobe with its relaxed fit. Wear them for any occasion, whether it's for daily life, streetwear, evening party, weekend, school, trip, hanging out, or shopping
